> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知大家又有冇呢啲趕飛機經歷呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎有啲時間打錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474cac00458ca3e6d611e1ab8865f1f115d35780","tid":630510,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"有次人在韓國首爾，想坐地鐵去仁川機場，諗住地鐵唔會塞車。<br />\n<br />\n點知我轉錯幾次車，每次都搭倒頭地鐵。<br />\n<br />\n好彩最後係起飛前1個鐘，趕到機場上機。"},{"pid":"a08956438e83d26917721edd65527c410ba3f6a3","tid":630510,"uid":136760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"架機7:45飛 你個朋友8:06到都仲有得搭，叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21079f1ad5579d42d2a7bc2edd26fa4776e4263f","tid":630510,"uid":88018,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a08956438e83d26917721edd65527c410ba3f6a3","tid":630510,"uid":136760,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"架機7:45飛 你個朋友8:06到都仲有得搭，叻叻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:26:41.000Z","msg":"打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係7:06"},{"pid":"772122ec2d18f27c490a591ab479e6ffae51f7ab","tid":630510,"uid":132296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d4df3177e68fd9ed34b6ae4dd4ba2a1d9bb4ba","tid":630510,"uid":66395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"無 <br />\n預早check in 係好基本"},{"pid":"e8527d66cb70001a012d4cc4d556726f9b1ec0a2","tid":630510,"uid":88018,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:35:53.000Z","msg":"補返當時一幅snap7<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/003508_5db812de7e570ca483723ce39605e12d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F003508_5db812de7e570ca483723ce39605e12d.png&h=a089e87f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"baa8d25bc5fd7355996038d3f1daa2858290a821","tid":630510,"uid":102589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:36:16.000Z","msg":"你個fd on9"},{"pid":"5714b17265320df456619aa7c33d9970dd99acc2","tid":630510,"uid":5375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T16:58:43.000Z","msg":"我習慣提早兩個鐘到機場，checkin完就同個朋友去醫醫肚先，<br />\n<br />\n個次唔知係咪撞鬼以為食完野就可以直接上機，食完係餐廳坐到剩返10分鐘先醒起未撚過關同安檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，咁梗係即刻狗衝啦，去到安檢排隊人唔算多，但好撚急，個食蕉堅持要我地正常安檢先，咁無辦法啦。去到海關人山人海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，即時同職員講要起飛了，就帶左我地去過個移民官既唔知乜通道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，過完關之後，係我地跑緊去閘口既同時，迎面有個女女地勤一邊講對講機一邊狗衝過黎問我地係咪呢班機，再同同事講我地黎緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，<br />\n<br />\n咁個次就無空橋既，一落到地見到成部巴士啲人等緊我地，7到好撚想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過好彩個地勤女女見到我地，如果唔係可能唔等我地了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957e97f71aab0800755ff3660c77e8e576cb4968","tid":630510,"uid":42338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"有次已經飛前3個半鐘出門口等機場巴士<br />\n去到巴士站啱啱好目送咗班車 見仲早就無追<br />\n正常廿分鐘一班 點知下一班等咗差唔多成粒鐘先到<br />\n膽粗粗第一次用網上check in <br />\n一落車即刻狗衝入閘<br />\n入閘後五分鐘就上機"},{"pid":"18127af3343da4136e89f7e5700dbb8103523733","tid":630510,"uid":154769,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:37:27.000Z","msg":"有次搵左個幾鐘，終於搵到啱心水嘅片<br />\n之後老母話到係樓下叫幫手拎嘢<br />\n之後趕到打10秒都冇就射左"},{"pid":"2582c0210d9e4a9e3eccb3edcf388a35a5bfd927","tid":630510,"uid":67617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/014347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F014347_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=efcd4f7f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a669fd37043e44e775dd8165cbf564ee12dba1d","tid":630510,"uid":24864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T17:49:21.000Z","msg":"唔知點解次次去機場都預唔岩時間 次次都要跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次係轉機 前一班遲佐 我地落機即刻狗衝去個閘 由0跑到5x <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑到扯撚晒蝦 不過最後都趕到"}]}